{"tid":2435401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"再有示威者遭槍殺  緬甸女子不畏死走上最前","createTime":"2021-03-06T08:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T08:20:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"43f98724bcaa94187ac6775f3ddb809e7847db9f","tid":2435401,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210306/G4IGP2J5ZFD2ZGS23UPEFPB6LI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210306%2FG4IGP2J5ZFD2ZGS23UPEFPB6LI%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=6585a9b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210306%2FG4IGP2J5ZFD2ZGS23UPEFPB6LI%2F&h=acba6ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210306/G4IGP2J5ZFD2ZGS23UPEFPB6LI/</a><br />\n<br />\n再有示威者遭槍殺 <br />\n緬甸女子不畏死走上最前<br />\n<br />\n緬甸反對軍政變示威再添亡魂，消息指軍隊昨天在第二大城市曼德勒又向手無寸鐵的遊行民眾開槍，至少一名示威者頸部中槍不治。這場波瀾壯闊的街頭抗爭運動，緬甸婦女撐起了半邊天，不少年輕女子更走在最前線，那怕付出沉重的代價，她們還是前仆後繼。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：緬軍圖轉走78億資金 遭美凍結<br />\n<br />\n年僅19歲的華裔少女鄧家希（瑪良烏）是周三被緬軍屠殺的38人之一，前日她在家鄉曼德勒舉殯，大批抗爭者在喪禮上舉起三指反專政手勢，送別這位英文名是「天使」（Angel）的女英雄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JVNOZUEHI7gDFHsob2TlNscZey4=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IDRDGQPA7NFPTPGTWFLN3ZZW6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJVNOZUEHI7gDFHsob2TlNscZey4%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIDRDGQPA7NFPTPGTWFLN3ZZW6Q.jpg&h=e5bae5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄧家希（左下）周三在曼德勒警察開槍時與其他示威者伏下，未幾頭部中槍死亡。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「天使」舉殯 遺言捐器官<br />\n<br />\n鄧家希上街前已有捨身成仁的準備，曾在社交媒體留言稱若遇上不測，希望捐出器官遺愛人間。<br />\n<br />\n鄧家希和政變後首位遇害的抗爭少女妙兌兌凱一樣，已成為緬甸示威者赤手空拳反抗軍事獨裁的象徵。傳統的緬甸社會不鼓勵。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸國防軍以極保守著稱，高層一位女將軍也沒有，基層士兵屢屢被指集體強。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n走上街頭的28歲女醫生尹茵茵說：「年輕女子擔起了示威大旗，在母性驅使下，我們不想下一代被摧毀，我們不怕死，只為了未來。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高掛包下身傳統服 震懾士兵<br />\n<br />\n這支游擊隊會用大批穿過的特敏，即緬甸婦女包裹下身的傳統服飾，在示威區上空拉起一幅巨型「八陣圖」，震懾趕來追捕示威者的緬軍，由於士兵通常都是迷信，害怕在特敏下經過會走霉運，於是當他們裹足不前之際，正好為抗爭者提供了逃走的黃金機會。<br />\n<br />\n周三的血腥鎮壓並未有嚇倒緬甸民眾，仰光、曼德勒、蒙育瓦、敏建、勃生等。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n繼fb和YouTube，TikTok也宣佈移除其平台上一些恐嚇緬甸示威者的親軍方片段。另外，緬甸昨日全國大停電，當局解釋是供電系統故障所致。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》/ 法新社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BxshxqQDVWU5v01NBrhGq54idrw=/1775x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RDKH7SHYX5CPXM3RNATAPC5OX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBxshxqQDVWU5v01NBrhGq54idrw%3D%2F1775x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRDKH7SHYX5CPXM3RNATAPC5OX4.jpg&h=49248ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■仰光女示威者用穿過的特敏拉起「結界」，阻止害怕在下面經過會走霉運的軍警追趕示威者。法新社"},{"pid":"a2714d304c50a1cc1d5049d72a3409cfe69e99dd","tid":2435401,"uid":178078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153a6d7ba2face907b595566241d063862154390","tid":2435401,"uid":260694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國，英國，中國，聯合國去撚咗邊！？"},{"pid":"0c619b6c64b4b442262ffee8599ba2c277bfc8f6","tid":2435401,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:17:11.000Z","msg":"佢地幾時有得移民？"},{"pid":"f86e194713985651be342f7d1d9f5a8b19d083eb","tid":2435401,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:17:56.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">這支游擊隊會用大批穿過的特敏，即緬甸婦女包裹下身的傳統服飾，在示威區上空拉起一幅巨型「八陣圖」，震懾趕來追捕示威者的緬軍，由於士兵通常都是迷信，害怕在特敏下經過會走霉運，於是當他們裹足不前之際，正好為抗爭者提供了逃走的黃金機會。</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757c21192fce15efb1d2c8976171d111fcac0e29","tid":2435401,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"尊敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181cdf823f2eb13d71970992d4ebcfe90e42708c","tid":2435401,"uid":173945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"153a6d7ba2face907b595566241d063862154390","tid":2435401,"uid":260694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國，英國，中國，聯合國去撚咗邊！？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:19:58.000Z","msg":"中國支持緬甸軍政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeaa3e9aeb9b7574a33f123ad0b12474d8ef5dd0","tid":2435401,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:20:01.000Z","msg":"佢地真係好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對實彈都唔退縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}